<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Pineridge</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">The Pineridge is a tranquil residential community in the North West Quadrant of Calgary. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">The community offers easy access to a variety of public amenities such as recreational venues, golf courses, shopping complexes and schools for its residents.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Built across a treeless prairie landscape, the Pineridge real estate now offers a huge variety of housing options ranging from single-family detached homes, row houses, bungalows and a few apartment condominiums that are readily available at an average price of $280,000.</p>
        </div>
